query:
SELECT o.id, o.status, o.totalSkus, o.processedSkus, oi.sku, oi.status as item_status, oi.errorMessage 
FROM orders o 
LEFT JOIN orderItems oi ON o.id = oi.orderId 
WHERE o.status = 'failed' 
ORDER BY o.id DESC LIMIT 10;
